long.ar,de,fr,ru:
If you're an user: Feed Proxy browser extension allows you to switch between many countries proxy servers in a click to watch or visit the geo-blocked contents.

If you're a developer or tester: Feed Proxy browser extension allows you to do your geo testing effectively, and quickly. You can quickly switch between countries proxy servers in a click.

Please, write your valuable review to enhance this extension and share with your colleagues and friends if you find this extension is helpful.

Also, take a look at my other extensions for Chrome and Firefox browsers.

For Chrome: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/search/d09r
For Firefox: https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/D09r/

long.zh_CN:
Feed Proxy is a Free Chrome Extension to Configure Advanced Proxy Settings and Manage Multiple Proxy Profiles.

Features:

# Multiple Custom Proxy Profiles
# Persistent Proxy Authentication
# Custom Proxy Profiles Supports Protocols HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, Socks4/ Socks5
# BypassList for Hosts to pass through without Proxy
# Default Profile of No Proxy (Direct Connection) and System Proxy Modes
# Rich Notifications with information of Proxy Profile, Server and Port on Proxy Profile Changes
# Auto Refresh the Current tab on Proxy Profile Changes
# Timer to disable Custom Proxy automatically to avoid Overage on Bill for excess bandwidth usage
# Multiple Languages Support, currently we include English, Spanish, Chinese, Hindi and more languages to come very soon
# Simple and Clean User Interface
# Backup Proxy Profiles and Preferences
# For Free!
